## Rangkuman Perubahan Per Warna

| Warna Lama | Warna Baru | Alasan |
|------------|------------|--------|
| `purple-600/700/800` | `hsl(var(--primary))` — Deep Sapphire | Design system primary color |
| `purple-50/100` (bg) | `hsl(var(--primary))/5~10` | Transparan dari primary |
| `indigo-600` | `hsl(var(--primary))` | Konsistensi design system |
| `indigo-50/30` (hover) | `hsl(var(--muted))/30` atau `bg-muted/30` | Hover state semantik |
| `gray-50/100/200/300/400/500/700/900` | Token semantik (`--foreground`, `--muted-foreground`, `--border`, `--card`, `--muted`) | Dark mode support |
| `bg-white` / `bg-gray-50` | `bg-[hsl(var(--card))]` / `bg-muted/50` | Dark mode support |
| Hex `#f8f6ff`, `#e0d9f7` | Token-based | Hardcoded hex → design system |
| `bg-blue-500` (avatar) | `bg-[hsl(var(--primary))]` | Konsistensi |

